<br />That is a great idea. Surprisingly, I hadn't thought of that yet. I was mostly thinking it was just for satisfaction. But yeah, difficulty level will definitely affect the ending now that you mention it. It might also affect the entire story throughout the game. Maybe there'll be different levels or something like that.
<br />
<br />However, what I'm wondering is what kinds of things will make the game more difficult. Like will enemies move faster, or will level design possibly change? Things like that. Any ideas would be nice. I am hoping for a simple (not necessarily lazy) and effective solution.</div>

					
