				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">An underused difficulty feature is different AI for enemies on different difficulty levels.
<br />
<br />For example, give enemies additional moves on higher difficulty levels.. or make their moves more sparatic and random so they're less predictable.  Or maybe even make them "smarter" and have them respond to player movements differently.
<br />
<br />Other staples of high difficulty levels:
<br />- Enemies take more hits to kill
<br />- More enemies (ie:  hide some enemies in Easy)
<br />- enemies hurt more
<br />- dropped items (life refills, etc) occur less frequently</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

